@startuml
title SD6 — Club Admin Updates Order Status (Mark Delivered)

actor ClubAdmin
participant "React Frontend" as React
participant OrderController
participant UpdateOrderStatusCommand
participant OrderRepository
participant OrderEventEmitter
participant NotificationObserver
participant NotificationRepository
participant MongoDB

ClubAdmin->React: Click "Mark Delivered" on Order Card
React->OrderController: PATCH /api/orders/:id/status { status: "delivered" }
OrderController->UpdateOrderStatusCommand: new UpdateOrderStatusCommand(id, "delivered")
UpdateOrderStatusCommand->OrderRepository: update(id, {status})
OrderRepository->MongoDB: updateOne(orders)
MongoDB-->OrderRepository: Order document
OrderRepository-->UpdateOrderStatusCommand: Order
UpdateOrderStatusCommand->OrderEventEmitter: emitOrderDelivered(order)
OrderEventEmitter->NotificationObserver: handleOrderDelivered(order)
NotificationObserver->NotificationRepository: create({userId, type:"order_delivered", message})
NotificationRepository->MongoDB: insertOne(notifications)
UpdateOrderStatusCommand-->OrderController: success
OrderController-->React: 200 OK
React-->ClubAdmin: UI updates order status to delivered

@enduml
